{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8103","title":"NG8103: Missing control flow directive\n\n缺少控制流指令","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8103.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive缺少控制流指令\">NG8103: Missing control flow directive\n\n缺少控制流指令<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive缺少控制流指令\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">此診斷可確保在範本中使用已知控制流指令（例如 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code> 、 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 、 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></code> ）的獨立元件也會單獨或藉助 <code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code> 匯入這些指令。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostics ensures that a standalone component which uses known control flow directives\n(such as <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code>, <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>, <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></code>) in a template, also imports those directives either\nindividually or by importing the <code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code>.</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\nstandalone: true,\n// Template uses `*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>`, but no corresponding directive imported.\ntemplate: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n// …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-fix-the-problem\" translation-result=\"on\">如何解決此問題<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#how-to-fix-the-problem\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">How to fix the problem<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8103#how-to-fix-the-problem\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">確保匯入了相應的控制流指令。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Make sure that a corresponding control flow directive is imported.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">指令可以單獨匯入：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A directive can be imported individually:</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\nimport {<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgIf</a>} from '@angular/common';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\nstandalone: true,\nimports: [<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgIf</a>],\ntemplate: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n// …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">或者匯入整個 <code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code>，其中包含所有控制流指令：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">or you could import the entire <code><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a></code>, which contains all control flow directives:</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\nimport {<a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a>} from '@angular/common';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\nstandalone: true,\nimports: [<a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a>],\ntemplate: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"visible\"&gt;Hi&lt;/div&gt;`,\n// …\n})\nclass MyComponent {}\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgSwitch\n - api/core/Component\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#how-to-fix-the-problem\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#ng8103-missing-control-flow-directive缺少控制流指令\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#如何解決此問題\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8103.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}